race.comment: TELLING (1) peaks for the Snowden yard and is ready to win. Went close at Scone last time at a short quote and Sherry takes over today. WRITTEN BY LUCY (5) races here rather than Canberra tomorrow and that a lead. Followed the Maiden win with a lip defeat at Nowra and she can control this contest jumping from an inside gate. Has upside and is a player. SABATINA (7) found more like her best winning a Narromine Maiden on the heavy. Back on track and a drier track will further advantage. She's back on track and is well in the mix. In the mix. SWEET FUTURE (4) showed enough early doors but hasn't warmed up in her three provincial starts this preparation. Drops back in grade on a quick backup and might be ready to show more.
